Service Value Chain	This is a central element of the SVS. It consists of activities like ‚ÄúPlan,‚Äù ‚ÄúImprove,‚Äù ‚ÄúEngage,‚Äù ‚ÄúDesign & Transition,‚Äù ‚ÄúObtain/Build,‚Äù ‚ÄúDeliver & Support.‚Äù The idea is that any service creation/delivery is a combination of these. 
freshworks.com
