Benefits of Adopting ITIL
Here are some of the commonly cited advantages (and what you should expect in practice):

Benefit	What it means / impact
Alignment with business goals	IT initiatives and services are tied to defined business value. Prevent IT from becoming a ‚Äúcost center‚Äù in the dark. 
