But here‚Äôs the catch:

You cannot work during this period.

You must leave the U.S. by the end of it unless you have a new valid status (which H-1B won‚Äôt activate until Oct 1).

So you‚Äôd still have a status gap of about 6 weeks before H-1B start ‚Äî meaning you‚Äôd need to leave the U.S. and re-enter with an H-1B visa.

